"The only queen with any power there is Woedica. I am told they erected an exquisite temple in her honor there, but I was never able to see it."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"Take care in your search. Many dangers lie in wait here."</DefaultText><FemaleText>"Take care in your search. Many dangers lie in wait here."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"Caed Nua will remain yours. It... could be great again... if you should wish it. Should we rebuild, you'll swiftly find that people will be drawn to your service."</DefaultText><FemaleText>"Caed Nua will remain yours. It... could be great again... if you should wish it. Should we rebuild, you'll swiftly find that people will be drawn to your service."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"That's not possible. Lord Raedric is dead. I saw to that." </DefaultText><FemaleText>"That's not possible. Lord Raedric is dead. I saw to that." </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"This must be some kind of trick." </DefaultText><FemaleText>"This must be some kind of trick." </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"I never turn down a challenge." </DefaultText><FemaleText>"I never turn down a challenge." </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"Oh, the messenger was very clear. Or perhaps I should say the letter was. Have a look, if you like." 

"I suppose it might be some kind of jest. Rather poor taste, isn't it?"</DefaultText><FemaleText>"Oh, the messenger was very clear. Or perhaps I should say the letter was. Have a look, if you like." 

"I suppose it might be some kind of jest. Rather poor taste, isn't it?"</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"Was there anything else I could do for you?" </DefaultText><FemaleText>"Was there anything else I could do for you?" </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"Who's that speaking?" </DefaultText><FemaleText>"Who's that speaking?" </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"You know what I am?" </DefaultText><FemaleText>"You know what I am?" </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"I'm sorry if I startled you. I'm afraid my manners have been slipping. I haven't had much opportunity for introductions, lately." 

