"In any case, I assume you're here looking for Maerwald?" </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"I've always wanted my own keep. Even if it is a little cursed." </DefaultText><FemaleText>"I've always wanted my own keep. Even if it is a little cursed." </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"He doesn't appear to be the kind to take 'no' for an answer, as it happens. I hope you'll be cautious, my lord. I don't know why this man means you harm, but he seems rather determined." </DefaultText><FemaleText>"He doesn't appear to be the kind to take 'no' for an answer, as it happens. I hope you'll be cautious, my lord. I don't know why this man means you harm, but he seems rather determined." </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"So I have heard. I am sure you will prevail, but I trust you will take precautions, even so. He seemed very intent on causing you harm." </DefaultText><FemaleText>"So I have heard. I am sure you will prevail, but I trust you will take precautions, even so. He seemed very intent on causing you harm." </FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"What do I want with a ruin?"</DefaultText><FemaleText>"What do I want with a ruin?"</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>The energy seems all at once to drain from the air. "It... is your decision, of course."

